## Technology Stack

| Layer | Tool | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| Agent LLM | Ollama with Qwen3.5-9B (or your choice) | Supports native tool calling; strong structured output for agentic tasks |
| Agent Framework | LangGraph or raw Ollama tool-calling loop | LangGraph for teams wanting structure; raw loop for teams wanting to understand the mechanics |
| Embeddings | nomic-embed-text via Ollama | For the `search_filings` tool's vector store |
| Vector Store | ChromaDB | Lightweight, in-process |
| Data Layer | Local JSON/CSV files | Sample portfolios, restricted list, compliance rules - all pre-loaded on device |
| UI | Gradio or Streamlit | Chat interface with a live "tool call trace" panel showing the agent's reasoning |
| Logging | MLflow + local JSON audit log | Every tool call, input, output, and decision logged |
| Dev Environment | VS Code + ZGX Toolkit extension | Use your own laptop; ZGX Nano handles all inference and compute |

