## Goals

By the end of the hackathon, your team should have:

- An agent that decomposes multi-part compliance queries into steps, calls the right tools, and produces coherent answers
- A visible decision trail: the trace sidebar shows every tool call and reasoning step so you can see the agent "think"
- A complete audit log: every action logged locally with timestamps, tool names, inputs, outputs, and reasoning
- Experience with the agentic development loop: tool schema design, prompt tuning, failure mode testing, and iterating fast on local compute

